Mongrethod Starting stats 4 Int, 5 Agi, 9 Str, base speed 320, base damage 9, Stats Gain per level 1.00 int, 1.20 str, 0.80 agi
Starting item Gaint Cleaver give 7 damage and 4% lifesteal base attack time 2.30 Auto-Attack,Tank,Mage

LEVEL 20 TALENT

Talent 1
increase Mongrethod health by 400 and his life regeneration by 5
increase Mongrethod armor by 1 for every 250 current life he got and his magic resist by 10% of his life renegeration

Talent 2
increase Mongrethod attack damage by 20 and his attack speed by 35
increase Mongrethod spell amp by 1% for every 10 current attack speed he got and increase his Rain of Fire Strenght scaling by 1% for
every 4 current attack Mongrethod got

PASSIVE D OR F PitLord
Increase overall stats and give a positive and negative buff

BUFF Mongrethod will gain 4 life per intelligence points and he also gets 10% damage reduction he also increase is strenght
by 30% of is intelligence he also start with a Special Ring Item that scale with every level. he can have 2 other Ring with this one
DEBUFF Mongrethod lose 50 attack speed and lose 40% of mana and he take 120% more damage from pure type,he cannot pass 350 basespeed and
he cannot use any-other weapons but Cleaver

UnderWorld Ring Special Item
increase spell amp by 7% increase by 0.2% every level
increase mana regeneration by 0.4 increase by 0.2 every level
increase life regeneration by 0.2 increase by 0.1 every level
can also be use to double the effect of the Ring for 10 second, cooldown of 90 second

talent level 25 upgrade PitLord
add a new modifier Chaos Lord
Mongrethod gain 20% spell amp with 15% armor increase he also gain 15% cooldown reduction and he now summon a permanent chaos Infernal
that got 80% of life and 280% damage of Mongrethod respawn every 60 second up to 2 max if they die, they will respawn after 60 second

SPELL Q Rain of Fire
Channel a raining wave of fire from the sky dealing damage and burn the enemy for a % of max health and current health for bosses
it also reduce the enemy movement speed every time they get damage by Rain of Fire

damage 11 15 19 23 plus 25% 28% 31% 34% of strenght per wave, damage type pure
burn damage 0.1% 0.3% 0.5% 0.7% of max Health, damage type magical per second
burn damage 0.1% 0.2% 0.3% 0.4% of current Health, damage type Pure per second for bosses
amount of waves 3 4 5 6
duration of channel 3 4 5 6
duration of burn damage and slow 2 second
